.com/nc/ugetab/nezplug.html|title=nezplug++|website=angelfire.com|accessdate=January 2, 2018}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoMZ-6\">[http://fantasyanime.com/emuhelp/music.htm#first_opening \"Several GSF-compatible Winamp Plugins\"]. ''Fantasy Anime'';</ref>\n<ref name=\"chip\">[http://www.chipamp.org/ \"Chipamp Winamp Plugin bundle\"] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100706121037/http://chipamp.org/ |date=July 6, 2010 }} Chipamp.com. Retrieved June 22, 2010.</ref>\n<ref name=\"Tidwell\">{{cite book| author=Tidwell, Jenifer| title=Designing Interfaces:Patterns for Effective Interaction Design |date=November 2005| publisher=[[O'Reilly Books]]| accessdate=June 23, 2010 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=5clhONg4UQIC&lpg=PA308 |isbn=978-0-596-00803-1}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Beggs\">{{cite book  |title=Designing Web Audio |author=Beggs, Josh and Thede, Dylan |year=2001 |page=191 |publisher=[[O'Reilly Media]]| isbn= 1-56592-353-7 |accessdate=June 22, 2010 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=EkCSeYHr134C&pg=PA190 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"SHacker\">{{cite book |author=Hacker, Scot |title=MP3: The Definitive Guide |publisher=[[O'Reilly Books]] |page=[https://archive.org/details/mp3definitivegui0000hack/page/141 141] |year=2000 |accessdate=June 23, 2010 |url=https://archive.org/details/mp3definitivegui0000hack |url-access=registration |isbn=1-56592-661-7}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoMZ-7\">As of June 2010, https://web.archive.org/web/20131219003427/http://www.winamp.com/skins lists over 1900 ''Classic'' skins and over 700 ''Modern'' skins.</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoMZ-8\">{{cite book| title=Interface Design: Effective Design of Graphical User Inferfaces |author= Dabbs, Alistair  |publisher=[[Watson-Guptill]] |year= 2002| isbn=0-8230-2516-0 |accessdate=June 22, 2010 |url=https://books.google.com/?id=lQ54VMjLMsYC&pg=RA5-PA10 }}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Hacker141\">Hacker, p.141.</ref>\n<ref name=\"AutoMZ-9\">As of June 2010, [http://1001Skins.com/ ''1001 Winamp Skins''] {{Webarchive|url=https